Package pp2016.team19.shared Description

Contains all shared classes.

Each class starting with prefix 'Mess' is a specific message to manage user interations coming from the GUI. All messages are derived form the abstrat class 'Message' Apart from that, classes are provided for the player, monster, poition, tile, wall, door, floor, highscore, key, labyrinth, node containing their specific attributes.

Author:
Goetz, Oliver, 5961343
